import { FormControl, FormLabel, VStack } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import React from 'react'

const Signup = () => {
  return (
      <VStack spacing='5px'>
          <FormControl>
              <FormLabel></FormLabel>
              <Input
                  placeholder='Enter Your Name'
                  
              
              />
          </FormControl>
          
    </VStack>
  )
}

export default Signup
